                <a href="/news/thank-you-guest-lecturer-and-meteorologist-john-ahrens-wsoc-tv">
                 <h3>
                  Thank you to guest lecturer and meteorologist John Ahrens from WSOC-TV!
                 </h3>
                </a>
                The Department of Psychological Science was proud to welcome WSOC-TV's meteorologist, John Ahrens, to our campus today.  He came to guest lecture in the Psychology of Acting senior capstone course (PSYC 4007).  John talked to students about life as a TV celebrity, what it is like to "act" on live TV, how he handles different weather situations, and what he does with the daily ratings he receives...
