                <a href="/news/welcome-start-fall-2018-semester">
                 <h3>
                  Welcome to the start of the Fall 2018 semester!
                 </h3>
                </a>
                Hello all and welcome back! 

 

From all of your advising team in the Department of Psychological Science, we wish you a productive and happy semester!  Please let us know if you need anything.  If you attended the Convocation lecture today with Dr. West, here is the copy of the lecture as well as a few other links and resources.  Again, let us know if you need guidance...
